properties.Name: MineIndicatedResource
properties.Description: Mine Indicated resources are the mine iron ore occurrences that have been sampled to a degree that an estimate has been made with reasonable confidence of their contained iron ore grade, tonnage, shape, densities and similar physical characteristics.
